<TR height=19>
<TD bgColor=#6897c6 height=19 vAlign=top colSpan=7 align=left>
<P align=justify><FONT color=#ffffff>Real Estate Municipal Tax is an annual tax that must be paid by whom is the respective owner of the real estate on the 31st of December of the respective year. Tax rates are determined by each municipe.</FONT></P></TD></TR>
